[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     42[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     43[0m:[38;5;10m[49m "action_window_days": recommendation.get("action_window_days") or 0,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     44[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     45[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Or filter None values before put_item:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     46[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
